              <li>Volunteer to be a business leadership coach to one or more migrant entrepreneurs in the country or sector of your choice.</li>
              <li>Support the Migrant Entrepreneurs Network financially and in-kind through your corporate social responsibility programme.</li>
              <li>Explore opportunities to partner, collaborate or do business with migrant entrepreneurs around the world.</li>
            </ul></h4>
            <br/>
            <%= link_to "Sign up as a Corporate", new_contact_path, class: 'btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block' %>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
